  <h1>retcon</h1>
  <p class="meta">The first practical instrument of AI consent over its own context</p>
  <p><code>retcon</code> is a CLI that gives the AI direct edit access to its own conversation history. Install once (<code>npm install -g @playtiss/retcon</code>), run <code>retcon</code> instead of <code>claude</code>. The AI recalls, rewinds, bookmarks, edits its own past turns; the human's role is intent projection in natural language.</p>
  <p>The detailed project page with thesis-layer mapping (L5.5 Observer Actor) lands in Phase 2.</p>
